"Page, Bill" <Bill.Page@drdc-rddc.gc.ca> writes:

| On Tuesday, August 01, 2006 10:12 PM Cliff Yapp wrote:
| > ...
| > I thought it would end up like this:
| > 
| > 1)  Have configure.ac and configure.ac.pamphlet both present 
