)abbrev domain MYIARR MyIndexedOneDimensionalArray
MyIndexedOneDimensionalArray(S:Type, mn:Integer):_
                 Exports == Implementation where
  Exports == OneDimensionalArrayAggregate S with
    myProperty

  Implementation == add
   minIndex x       == mn


