"Page, Bill" <Bill.Page@drdc-rddc.gc.ca> writes:

> Gaby, 
> 
> On Tuesday, August 29, 2006 5:27 PM you wrote:
> > 
> >   GCL-2.6.9pre, checkout of cvs as of this morning, has problems
> > making new lisp image.  More precisely, the instruction
